item.title: S8 Ep64: Alex Young, star of Cold War, Standing At The Sky's Edge & Follies
item.description:
Alex Young is currently appearing in Cold War at the Almeida Theatre.

Based on Paweł Pawlikowski’s film, Cold War is described as an epic love story spanning the decades and breadth of Europe at its most divided. The show features traditional Polish songs alongside music from Elvis Costello and is adapted by Conor McPherson with direction from Rupert Goold... Feed: https://feeds.buzzsprout.com/561565.rss
